ng="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/NoelGallagher-The-Beatles-supergroup-Paul-McCartney-Ringo-Starr.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/NoelGallagher-The-Beatles-supergroup-Paul-McCartney-Ringo-Starr-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/NoelGallagher-The-Beatles-supergroup-Paul-McCartney-Ringo-Starr-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/NoelGallagher-The-Beatles-supergroup-Paul-McCartney-Ringo-Starr-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/NoelGallagher-The-Beatles-supergroup-Paul-McCartney-Ringo-Starr-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/NoelGallagher-The-Beatles-supergroup-Paul-McCartney-Ringo-Starr-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔</a>曾表示，他想与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>的幸存成员一起加入一个超级团体。</p><p>这位独唱家和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲乐队</a>成员长期以来一直引用披头士四人组对他音乐的影响，并此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-on-how-embarrassing-it-was-for-oasis-to-be-compared-to-the-beatles-3097649">表示这支传奇乐队“对我来说意味着一切”</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/noel-gallagher-live-in-london-oasis-setlist-3474962">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 伦敦现场演出：绿洲经典在重聚传闻中大放异彩</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在 1995 年，加拉格尔就与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-weller">保罗·韦勒</a>联手录制了披头士乐队经典歌曲《Come Together》的翻唱。这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying Birds</a>音乐家还在 2021 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-says-he-teamed-up-with-paul-mccartney-for-a-duet-at-stella-mccartneys-50th-birthday-3050807">Stella McCartney 的 50 岁生日派对上与 Macca 合作进行了二重唱</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/noel-gallagher-dreams-forming-ultimate-30667460" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《镜报》</em></a>援引加拉格尔的话说，他“肯定会与麦卡特尼和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈斯塔尔</a>一起加入一个超级组合”。</p><p> “我不知道我是否会开始一个，”他解释道。 “我想和谁一起加入超级组合？<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-347-1271210">我可以轻松地与 [Paul] Weller 组成乐队，也可以与 Johnny [Marr] 组成乐队</a>。”</p><p>加拉格尔补充道：“弹贝斯……林戈和麦卡真是太棒了。</p><p> “想象一下与 Ringo 和 Macca 组成一个乐队。谁在唱歌？每个人。我他妈愿意花钱参与其中。给我[发起人]哈维·戈德史密斯。” </p><figure id="attachment_3476102" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3476102" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3476102" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/paul-mccartney@2000x1270.jpg" alt="保罗·麦卡特尼在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/paul-mccartney@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/paul-mccartney@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/paul-mccartney@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/paul-mccartney@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/paul-mccartney@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/paul-mccartney@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3476102" class="wp-caption-text">保罗·麦卡特尼现场表演。图片来源：哈利·杜兰特/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>去年十月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-on-the-beatles-cultural-power-theyre-a-level-above-3337474">加拉格尔表示，披头士乐队在文化力量方面仍保持“高水平”</a> 。</p><p>当被问及他是否曾与披头士乐队的任何成员谈论过歌曲创作时，他回答说：“不，我并没有真正与其他歌曲作者谈论过歌曲创作，因为你会说什么？我只是认为每个人都是一样的，只是有些人比其他人更有才华。”</p><p>在最近的新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-struggles-remember-need-teleprompter-3481552">加拉格尔透露，他现在在舞台上表演时很难记住歌曲的歌词</a>。他解释说，将来会考虑使用提词器，并说：“我确信，最终我会需要一个。”</p><p>与此同时，加拉格尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds-announce-2023-uk-arena-tour-3421081">今年将开始英国巡演</a>，以支持他最新的 High Flying Birds 专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds-council-skies-review-3450645">《Council Skies》</a> 。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/noel-gallagher-s-high-flying-birds-tickets/artist/1637030?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=TUeRTURCWxyNT8CXSVXWIUg%3AUkF1KK2fiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到任何剩余的门票</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-wants-to-join-a-supergroup-with-the-surviving-beatles-3481592">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 希望与幸存的披头士乐队 (Beatles) 一起加入超级组合的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
